{
  "stem": "10960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot, because her last name was different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Perhaps, because she had the suitcases of mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I [? brother ?] [? worked ?] there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also, I gave them my sister's belongings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told her, if anyone from the [? mandal ?] cares, will remain alive, she shall give it to them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I still don't know who took it there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Who cares?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think that cousin of his took all of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she answered me the letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She said, like we know which one is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, like I see you don't know anything from your husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I received several letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This what she wrote.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But she didn't indicate his-- his place of living, where in Russia?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Russia is big, large.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I mailed her a registered letter, [NON-ENGLISH], you know, like a certified [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Listen, I paid for everything, because I worked, so I use to get money and this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I said, I begged that she should write to me a letter where in Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I am in Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Where in Russia?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She didn't answered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So then I decided to take myself, to change my passport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because I couldn't get out from-- from that hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was an army hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was thinking maybe my-- my husband is there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But, so then I-- I went to the passport office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And here I made friends with a woman, the main woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Although there it was a policeman, I-- I just walked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He asked me what I want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I said, oh, I'm waiting for my friends, this, that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here, I-- I walked over to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a ring, which my mother-in-law, [NON-ENGLISH], she gave me a beautiful ring.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like this.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
